    <title>The ExtraRoute Extension</title>
    <para>ExtraRoute</para>
    <para>
        You can setup route configration on the Router using this extension.
        This extension augment the 'Router' resource by adding a new 'routes' attribute.
        NOTE: The attribute is called 'routes' not 'route'.
    </para>
    <para>
        We can specify a set of ip of nexthop and cidr of destination.
        Note the nexthop ip should be connected via one router interface.
        This is why configration of route property is allowed only on update time.
    </para>
   <table rules="all">
       <caption>Router Attributes</caption>
       <col width="20%"/>
       <col width="8%"/>
       <col width="10%"/>
